        "id": 1006192
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-03-26T13:55:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Unrelated: we may want to also move JGroups to a separate forwarder and different plugin, so that `high-availability` won\u0027t depend on external libs anymore.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 91,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 91,
        "endChar": 11
