        "id": 1006192
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-03-26T13:55:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We do we need to configure it? If you have another plugin that binds the forwarder, then it should automatically apply.\n\nAdding a `NoForwarder` seems an unnecessary step to me.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 68,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 71,
        "endChar": 74
      },
      "revId": "5848b49249d470ed65738b857ad5bb85068f179d",
      "serverId": "173816e5-2b9a-37c3-8a2e-48639d4f1153"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
